Usage: ./scripts/run-complete-validation.sh [OPTIONS]

Complete UV Migration Validation Orchestrator

Options:
    --fast              Skip optional checks (faster execution)
    --ci                CI/CD mode (minimal output)
    --stop-on-fail      Stop on first failure
    --skip-docker       Skip Docker build validation
    --skip-security     Skip security scans
    --verbose, -v       Enable verbose output
    --help, -h          Show this help message

Examples:
    ./scripts/run-complete-validation.sh                      # Full validation
    ./scripts/run-complete-validation.sh --fast               # Quick validation
    ./scripts/run-complete-validation.sh --ci                 # CI/CD pipeline
    ./scripts/run-complete-validation.sh --stop-on-fail       # Fail fast mode

Exit codes:
    0 - All validations passed
    1 - UV setup failed
    2 - Docker build failed
    3 - Production validation failed
    4 - Configuration validation failed
    5 - Multiple failures
